plot:
15-year-old Ida lives with her mother in Rossö in the Strömstad 
archipelago. Over the course of three stormy days, her life is turned 
upside down. She has a strained relationship with her mother, a 
non-existent relationship with her father and is let down by her best 
friend.
title: Håll om mig
